Current openCV (v.4.2.0) installed location in dan@dan-VirtualBox:~/build using python3

Installment:
:~ $ sudo apt-get -y install python3-pip
:~ $ pip3 isntall --upgrade pip
:~ $ mkdir build
:~ $ cd build
:~/build $ pip3 install opencv-python 

Verify
:~/build $ python3
>>> import cv2 as cv
>>> print(cv.__version__)
